window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Looking for something? Lucy Corentine, the Vampire Detective, is here to help! </p> <p>Lucy's always been looking for a quiet life away from vampire society, and doing her PI work. But when a box with a blind cat, and her semi-fianc√© turn up all in the same week, she begins to unravel a mystery unlike any other. </p> <p>When someone hires her to find a missing watch, she thinks things have taken a turn for the better...she doesn't know how wrong she is. </p> <p>Fangs For Nothing is book one of the complete Vampire Detective Trilogy, an urban fantasy mystery series with a quirky heroine, a blind cat, and a romantic whychoose subplot.</p>"; 
